WEBVTT

00:01.468 --> 00:04.169
He's got a job as a lollipop man!
'Course he has.

00:04.238 --> 00:07.717
I'm gay. Of course I know,
you're my best mate.

00:07.718 --> 00:09.877
I like being around you.

00:09.878 --> 00:12.877
So, is there anything going
on between you and Liam, then? No.

00:12.878 --> 00:14.918
I've sort of got a date this Friday.

00:21.278 --> 00:25.278
Well, we've got a full team.

